fields.abstract: Anthony DeCurtis interviews record executive Clive Davis, who signed such legendary artists as Janis Joplin and Santana, and who founded Arista Records. Part I: Early Life and Career Part II: Colombia Records etc. Part III: Janis Joplin Part IV: Simon and Garfunkel and Santana
